    "id": "v1"
  }, "v1"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA ph\xE1n, \"H\u1EE1i d\xE2n Gia-c\u1ED1p, c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\xE0 \u0111\u1EA7y t\u1EDB ta. H\xE3y nghe ta \u0111\xE2y! H\u1EE1i d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en, ta \u0111\xE3 ch\u1ECDn ng\u01B0\u01A1i.\" "), mdx("h6", {
